{
  "texts": [
    "This classification was based on whether the statements provoked actions of violence or discrimination.",
    "The categorization into moderately hateful and hateful was influenced by definitions established in studies by Sanguinetti et al. [63] and Sharma et al.",
    "According to these definitions, utterances explicitly encouraging violence or discriminatory actions were classified as severely hateful.",
    "The degree of severity remained unchanged whether the authors merely justified such actions, expressed a desire for their occurrence, or showed a willingness to partake in them.",
    "Consequently, any utterances that in any manner incited such actions were included in this most severe category."
  ]
}